loach.ui.midp2
Class MIDP2LoachUI

java.lang.Object
  javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet
      loach.ui.midp2.MIDP2LoachUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
Disposable
public final class MIDP2LoachUI
extends javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet
implements Disposable

Loach Mobile - MIDP2LoachUI Loach Mobile is ruled by the view, rather than the model. Therefore, this enables you to have the view as the kickstart, starting up various parts of the model as the view needs to, and then listening in to broadcasted events.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Chris Dennett
